THIS IS A VERY BOLD, MILITARY

00:00:47.714 --> 00:00:49.716
ASSESSMENT, THAT THIS AMOUNT OF

00:00:49.716 --> 00:00:52.652
CIVILIAN KILLING IS GOING TO

00:00:52.652 --> 00:00:54.821
LEAD NOT ONLY TO THIS TRAGEDY

