&gt;&gt; I THINK HE'S RIGHT, AND I

00:01:06.866 --> 00:01:08.668
THINK WHAT YOU SEE IS A TENSION

00:01:08.668 --> 00:01:09.869
BETWEEN THOSE OF US WHO HAVE

00:01:09.869 --> 00:01:10.937
WORKED IN POLITICAL AND

00:01:10.937 --> 00:01:12.038
MILITARY FIELDS ON THE GROUND,

00:01:12.038 --> 00:01:13.840
IN THE MIDDLE EAST, AND IN THE

00:01:13.840 --> 00:01:15.642
DEFENSE ESTABLISHMENT IN THE

00:01:15.642 --> 00:01:16.743
UNIFORM SERVICES, WHO

00:01:16.743 --> 00:01:17.944
UNDERSTAND THAT THIS IS NOT

00:01:17.944 --> 00:01:18.745
GOING TO WORK.

00:01:18.745 --> 00:01:20.046
THIS IS NOT GOING TO LEAD TO

00:01:20.046 --> 00:01:21.781
THE RESULT THAT ISRAEL WANTS,

00:01:21.781 --> 00:01:23.016
IT IS JUST GOING TO PROLONG THE

00:01:23.016 --> 00:01:25.752
SUFFERING OF BOTH THE ISRAELI

00:01:25.752 --> 00:01:26.052
--

00:01:26.052 --> 00:01:27.887
FOR ANOTHER GENERATION.

