AS OPPOSED TO A VERY POLITICAL,

00:01:31.825 --> 00:01:32.792
IDEOLOGICAL PERSPECTIVE, THAT

00:01:32.792 --> 00:01:33.893
IS COMING FROM THE POLITICAL

00:01:33.893 --> 00:01:35.829
LEVEL IN THE U.S. AND IN ISRAEL,

00:01:35.829 --> 00:01:36.729
AND IN THE UK.

00:01:36.729 --> 00:01:38.731
THAT THINKS THERE IS A WAY TO

00:01:38.731 --> 00:01:39.833
MAKE THIS WORK.

00:01:39.833 --> 00:01:41.067
THERE IS NOT, AND THE SUFFERING

00:01:41.067 --> 00:01:42.068
WE HAVE SEEN ON THE GROUND

00:01:42.068 --> 00:01:43.002
REALLY REFLECTS THAT.

