I CAN'T RECALL A TIME IN MY

00:01:45.672 --> 00:01:46.773
EXPERIENCE, WE HAVE SEEN SUCH A

00:01:46.773 --> 00:01:48.775
DISCONNECT BETWEEN OUR VALUES

00:01:48.775 --> 00:01:51.711
