00:01:51.711 --> 00:01:53.680
PERSPECTIVES OF POLITICAL

00:01:53.680 --> 00:01:55.915
LEADERSHIP, AT THE REALITIES ON

00:01:55.915 --> 00:01:56.783
THE GROUND.

