THEY ARE ENABLING THIS KILLING.

00:02:52.071 --> 00:02:54.073
&gt;&gt; THIS IS AMERICAN POLICY,

00:02:54.073 --> 00:02:55.975
IT'S NOT LIKE THESE ARE ROGUE

00:02:55.975 --> 00:02:56.409
TRANSFERS.

